118 (i) The department and the Department of Revenue may
119 adopt rules to implement and administer this act.
120 (j)(1) The tax credit allowed under this act may be
121 claimed beginning with the 2027 tax year.
122 (2) This tax credit may not be claimed after tax year
123 2031.
124 Section 2. This act shall become effective on June 1,
125 2026.
